      <title>来自微软的大宝贝 Windows Terminal</title>
      <link href="/terminal/"/>
      <url>/terminal/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>万物起于Terminal，那也就让Terminal为本博客做开篇吧。我是一个重度终端用户，每天都要用到终端，因此拥有一个好看且顺手的终端自然是必不可少的。在写这篇文章之前我也翻阅了不少文档及博客，但他们都有一个共病，那就是一旦这些插件更换了地址代码就自然会失效，就固然给新手带来了许多麻烦，而且也不标注出处<del>（此处请容许我暴打这些作者）</del>，因此还是放在自己这里好，也方便下次使用。</p><h2 id="选用"><a href="#选用" class="headerlink" title="选用"></a>选用</h2><p>作为一个软粉自然要使用自家的软件啦，这里选用PowerShell 7 + Oh My Posh作为终端环境，微软在Build 2019开发者大会上公布了自家最新的<code>Windows Terminal</code>并宣布开源该项目，此外支持WSL及其他终端。从此<code>Cmd</code>与传统<code>PowerShell</code>的时代也逐渐走向尽头，目前该项目在<a href="https://github.com/microsoft/Terminal">GitHub</a>开源，并提供多种安装方式。</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/GzaUtiTfVoPLyjJ.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/Zeqz5NbQL17VtW2.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/MEIezLd5w82jloW.jpg" alt="Microsoft Store 截图"></p><h2 id="安装Windows-Terminal"><a href="#安装Windows-Terminal" class="headerlink" title="安装Windows Terminal"></a>安装Windows Terminal</h2><h4 id="通过-Microsoft-Store-推荐"><a href="#通过-Microsoft-Store-推荐" class="headerlink" title="通过 Microsoft Store [推荐]"></a>通过 Microsoft Store [推荐]</h4><p><a href="https://aka.ms/terminal">Windows Terminal from the Microsoft Store</a></p><h4 id="通过-GitHub"><a href="#通过-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="通过 GitHub"></a>通过 GitHub</h4><p>从<a href="https://github.com/microsoft/terminal/releases">Releases page</a>下载<code>Microsoft.WindowsTerminal_&lt;versionNumber&gt;.msixbundle</code> （使用此方式安装将<strong>不会自动更新</strong>）</p><h4 id="通过-WPM"><a href="#通过-WPM" class="headerlink" title="通过 WPM"></a>通过 WPM</h4><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">winget install -<span class="literal">-id</span>=Microsoft.WindowsTerminal <span class="literal">-e</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="通过-Scoop（非官方）"><a href="#通过-Scoop（非官方）" class="headerlink" title="通过 Scoop（非官方）"></a>通过 Scoop（非官方）</h4><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop bucket add extras <span class="comment"># Stable</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop install windows<span class="literal">-terminal</span> <span class="comment"># Stable</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop bucket add <span class="string">&#x27;ash258.ash258&#x27;</span> <span class="string">&#x27;https://github.com/Ash258/Shovel-Ash258.git&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># Preview</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop install WindowsTerminal<span class="literal">-preview</span> <span class="comment"># Preview</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>P.S.通过此方式安装的Windows Terminal将无法设置为默认终端,如遇到任何安装/更新问题请在<a href="https://github.com/lukesampson/scoop-extras/issues">Issues page</a>提交Issues</em></p><h4 id="通过-Chocolatey（非官方）"><a href="#通过-Chocolatey（非官方）" class="headerlink" title="通过 Chocolatey（非官方）"></a>通过 Chocolatey（非官方）</h4><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">choco install microsoft<span class="literal">-windows</span><span class="literal">-terminal</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装新版-PowerShell"><a href="#安装新版-PowerShell" class="headerlink" title="安装新版 PowerShell"></a>安装新版 PowerShell</h2><p>参考：<a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/scripting/install/installing-powershell-core-on-windows?view=powershell-7.1">微软PowerShell安装文档</a></p><p>Windows 10自带的PowerShell为PowerShell 5，两者为共存关系，无法覆盖</p><h4 id="通过-Microsoft-Store-推荐-1"><a href="#通过-Microsoft-Store-推荐-1" class="headerlink" title="通过 Microsoft Store [推荐]"></a>通过 Microsoft Store [推荐]</h4><p><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/store/apps/9MZ1SNWT0N5D">Stable版本</a> <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/zh-cn/p/powershell-preview/9p95zzktnrn4">Preview版本</a></p><h4 id="通过-GitHub-1"><a href="#通过-GitHub-1" class="headerlink" title="通过 GitHub"></a>通过 GitHub</h4><p><a href="https://aka.ms/powershell-release?tag=stable">Stable版本</a> <a href="https://aka.ms/powershell-release?tag=preview">Preview版本</a></p><p><code>PowerShell-&lt;version&gt;-win-x64.msi</code>，无脑Next即可</p><ul><li><p>默认安装目录为<code>$env:ProgramFiles\PowerShell\&lt;version&gt;</code></p></li><li><p>启动目录为<code>$env:ProgramFiles\PowerShell\&lt;version&gt;\pwsh.exe</code></p></li><li><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/lXANdvIRyHh2ZxY.png"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/9AHMKTcgQvGsBqP.png"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/IzHPyBm1964hZKY.png" alt="无脑回车即可"></p></li></ul><h4 id="通过WPM安装"><a href="#通过WPM安装" class="headerlink" title="通过WPM安装"></a>通过WPM安装</h4><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">winget install -<span class="literal">-name</span> PowerShell -<span class="operator">-exact</span></span><br><span class="line">winget install -<span class="literal">-name</span> PowerShell<span class="literal">-Preview</span> -<span class="operator">-exact</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="通过-Scoop（非官方）-1"><a href="#通过-Scoop（非官方）-1" class="headerlink" title="通过 Scoop（非官方）"></a>通过 Scoop（非官方）</h4><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop install powershell <span class="comment"># Stable</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop install powershell<span class="literal">-preview</span> <span class="comment"># Preview</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>P.S.使用此方式安装的 PowerShell 需手动添加至 Windows Terminal</strong></p><p>抱歉，我使用Scoop，请Chocolatey用户自行摸索</p><h2 id="安装Oh-My-Posh"><a href="#安装Oh-My-Posh" class="headerlink" title="安装Oh My Posh"></a>安装Oh My Posh</h2><blockquote><p>参考：<a href="https://ohmyposh.dev/docs/pwsh">Oh My Posh Docs</a></p></blockquote><p>打开Windows Terminal，如果你从Microsoft Store或者GitHub安装PowerShell，默认终端已经配置为PowerShell 7</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/Sz7NZEmTfjg52WU.png" alt="初始样式"></p><p>macOS及Linux用户一定也知道<a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh">Oh my zsh</a>项目，<a href="https://github.com/JanDeDobbeleer/oh-my-posh">Oh My Posh</a>也是一个优秀的终端优化的项目</p><p>执行以下命令安装Oh My Posh</p><p><code>Install-Module oh-my-posh -Scope CurrentUser</code></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/cF9W5Ys2RXGderp.png"></p><p>输入<code>y</code>回车即可（从不被信任的仓库安装）</p><h2 id="配置Oh-My-Posh"><a href="#配置Oh-My-Posh" class="headerlink" title="配置Oh My Posh"></a>配置Oh My Posh</h2><p>使用Notepad对PowerShell默认启动脚本进行配置，提示不存在点击“是<code>创建Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1</code>文件，目录在<code>C:\Users\Username\Documents\PowerShell</code></p><p>输入以下内容并保存</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Import-Module</span> <span class="built_in">oh</span><span class="literal">-my</span><span class="literal">-posh</span> <span class="comment"># 导入 Oh My Posh模块</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Set-PoshPrompt</span> <span class="literal">-Theme</span> ys <span class="comment"># 设置主题为 ys</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Set-PSReadLineOption</span> <span class="literal">-PredictionSource</span> <span class="built_in">History</span> <span class="comment"># 使用历史记录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Set-PSReadLineKeyHandler</span> <span class="literal">-Key</span> UpArrow <span class="literal">-Function</span> HistorySearchBackward <span class="comment"># 上键使用上次输入内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Set-PSReadLineKeyHandler</span> <span class="literal">-Key</span> DownArrow <span class="literal">-Function</span> HistorySearchForward <span class="comment"># 下键查找历史记录</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>更多主题执行<code>Get-PoshThemes</code>或访问<a href="https://ohmyposh.dev/docs/themes">Themes</a></p></blockquote><p>更改主题后可能会出现字体乱码的情况，我们可以安装PL字体进行解决，主流的字体有<a href="https://www.nerdfonts.com/">Nerd Fonts</a>,<a href="https://github.com/microsoft/cascadia-code">Cascadia Code</a>等等，我这里使用[Cascadia Code](<a href="https://github.com/microsoft/cascadia-code">microsoft/cascadia-code: This is a fun, new monospaced font that includes programming ligatures and is designed to enhance the modern look and feel of the Windows Terminal. (github.com)</a>)进行演示</p><h3 id="安装Cascadia-Code"><a href="#安装Cascadia-Code" class="headerlink" title="安装Cascadia Code"></a>安装Cascadia Code</h3><h4 id="通过-GitHub-2"><a href="#通过-GitHub-2" class="headerlink" title="通过 GitHub"></a>通过 GitHub</h4><p>在Releases页面找到<code>CascadiaCode-&lt;version&gt;.zip</code>，下载后解压<code>ttf</code>文件夹内所有文件右键<code>Install for all users</code></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/btWpqGZ5hcswumS.png"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/zr64SHgnvNPO3yu.png" alt="安装"></p><h4 id="通过-Scoop"><a href="#通过-Scoop" class="headerlink" title="通过 Scoop"></a>通过 Scoop</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop bucket add nerd-fonts</span><br><span class="line">scoop install Cascadia-Code</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="美化及调整操作习惯"><a href="#美化及调整操作习惯" class="headerlink" title="美化及调整操作习惯"></a>美化及调整操作习惯</h2><p>点击下箭头Settings &gt; 将 Default terminal application 更改为刚刚安装的 Windows Terminal 并点击保存（以后不再赘述）</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/RjOLEq4DQvAr9VY.png">打开 <code>Show acrylic in tab row (requires relauch)</code></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/HXtjSeCyDEi8U9q.png"></p><p>切换Color schemes为<code>One Half Light</code>，并将Font face更换为<code>Cascadia Mono PL</code>，将Font Size调整为<code>12</code>，Font weight调整为<code>Semi-light</code>打开<code>Arcylic</code>选项，将<code>Arcylic opacity</code>调整为50%</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/3DQMGuqNeUXjZwb.png"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/3rlmaN4xAciVEwT.png"></p><p>隐藏旧版本<code>PowerShell</code>及<code>Azure Cloud Shell</code></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/3SZPOJGRaArMhWf.png"></p><p>至此关于 Windows Terminal 的调教基本完成，现在我们来配置VS Code</p><h2 id="调整-VS-Code-字体"><a href="#调整-VS-Code-字体" class="headerlink" title="调整 VS Code 字体"></a>调整 VS Code 字体</h2><p>按下Ctrl + Shift + P 输入Open Settings，点击第一个</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/01/id6pGswNkcynBY2.png"></p><blockquote><p> “editor.fontWeight”: 350,</p><p>“editor.fontSize”: 15.5,</p><p>“editor.fontFamily”: “Cascadia Mono”,</p></blockquote><p>将上述内容粘贴保存即可</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
